name: Fives - Card Game
description: Poker, Spades, Bid, Uno and Black Jack are some of the most popular and unique card games around the world. So if you like playing those, you will love playing FIVES. FIVES is the new card game that’s sure to become one of the hottest addictive games ever played. FIVES is fun, fast paced and competitive.  Everyone will enjoy playing this sure to be classic card game FIVES!
